ivardefs.name: fraction
ivardefs.desc: This element is capturing information about the fraction of a plant part, or human plasma for fractionation.

ivardefs.name: materialType
ivardefs.desc: The specific type of the material constituting the component. For Herbal preparations the particulars of the extracts (liquid/dry) is described in Specified Substance Group 1.
